{"tid":1022935,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跑山撞正 美國男徒手打死美洲獅","createTime":"2019-02-15T11:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T11:42:48.000Z","uid":24536,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"626d27a9dd561a49aad21fceee404148a013efb0","tid":1022935,"uid":24536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9BBrRRcrZCA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9BBrRRcrZCA&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf5X8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=e3309e1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9BBrRRcrZCA</a><br />\n<br />\n好痴線 講到輕描淡寫 但其實真係好好彩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbb0ecc091dcb6fc549905b2ab3af0adcfb68b9","tid":1022935,"uid":24536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T11:28:45.000Z","msg":"Kauffman saw the mountain lion roughly 10 feet away. He threw his hands up in the air and started yelling. The mountain lion kept approaching, and eventually, lunged at him.<br />\n<br />\nThe cat latched its jaw onto Kauffman&rsquo;s right wrist, the runner said. Kauffman tried to protect his face as the mountain lion clawed at him.<br />\n<br />\nThroughout the attack, Kauffman said he was doing his &rdquo;barbarian yell as best I could,&ldquo; and tried throwing the cat off him &mdash; which led to them both tumbling down a slope.<br />\n<br />\n&rdquo;From there it was just like a <strong>wrestling match</strong> &mdash; it was thrashing and it still had my wrist locked in its jaws,&ldquo; Kauffman said. He added that he pinned down the cat&lsquo;s back legs using his left knee.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.foxnews.com/us/man-says-killing-mountain-lion-with-bare-hands-was-just-like-a-wrestling-match.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fus%2Fman-says-killing-mountain-lion-with-bare-hands-was-just-like-a-wrestling-match.amp&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf5X8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=b5beb786\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.foxnews.com/us/man-says-killing-mountain-lion-with-bare-hands-was-just-like-a-wrestling-match.amp</a>"},{"pid":"c0d096964d69382f09c08f8dbd86f33f93712c64","tid":1022935,"uid":24536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T11:30:09.000Z","msg":"連登仔一拳一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2e8a4127b5ef51ee391138cd6ac776c3c14a1e","tid":1022935,"uid":24536,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T11:33:12.000Z","msg":"中文版:<br />\n<br />\n美國男子考夫曼（Travis Kauffman）最近爆紅！因日前他在山區慢跑時遭遇美洲獅襲擊，讓他為了存活極力反擊，最後徒手將獅子打死，日前經過一段時間休養後，還原了當時死裡逃生過程，讓民眾聽了都不盡替他捏把冷汗。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，考夫曼回憶表示，4日他在馬齒山（Horsetooth Mountain）跑步時，隱約停建在背後發出沙沙聲，不料轉頭赫然驚見一隻美洲獅離他超近約不到3公尺，隨後他立即遭美洲獅襲擊，其一隻手臂被美洲獅咬住，這讓他恐懼瞬間轉換成激烈的求生慾，並試圖將美洲獅甩開，結果雙雙跌落山坡。<br />\n<br />\n考夫曼指出，兩人跌落後美洲獅疑似被這一摔驚嚇，不過手臂能被美洲獅咬住，他並隨手抓起附近樹枝和岩石當武器，對著美洲獅頭部、喉部亂打，最後美洲獅終於鬆口，讓他立即改變型態，利用右腳鎖住美洲獅脖子，沒過多久美洲獅便窒息死亡，之後他又延小徑又跑了約4.8公里後幸運遇上另一名跑者，在對方協助下到了停車場，在一對好心夫婦幫助下送往醫院治療。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，<strong>考夫曼臉頰救縫了19針、鼻梁縫了6針，手臂則是3針</strong>。對此，科羅拉多公園及野生動物部門表示，該美洲獅大約4到5個月大，體重約在約16公斤至18公斤，死因於鈍器創傷和窒息等多重原因。當時當局還讚賞考夫曼做法正確，且呼籲如遇到此事件，因仿考夫曼作法引發討論。<br />\n<br />\n14日考夫曼在記者會上說明事情經過，讓許多聽眾都替他捏把冷汗，不過在被問起是否之後會再去跑步，他表示：「會再回到那條小徑跑步，不過會與朋友一起。」並強調「科羅拉多州是一個獨一無二的州，可以看到真正的野生動物，不過遠遠的看就好了啦。」<br />\n<br />\n[url<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/hk.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/%25E5%25BE%2592%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E7%258D%2585-%25E8%2582%2589%25E6%2590%258F%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B-103533435.html[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Famphtml%2F%